      "writtenOn": "2020-03-23T14:17:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "On ARM, the equivalent feature may always be enabled.\n\nActually, this sysctl is gone on 10.15 (I think that’s the version) for x86_64 too. We should just treat it as “true” on x86_64 macOS if the OS is new enough.",
