        "id": 1116294
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-03-24T21:57:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It can only ever be x86_64?  systemsnapshotios already knows that at compile-time.\n\nI could expose interfaceidiom, but it\u0027s pretty analogous to what arm returns for uts.machine, so I figured I would mirror this here.",
      "parentUuid": "cb940403_9109e2f8",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 79,
